## Personalisation Checklist

Before sending, verify:

- [ ] Company name is spelled correctly (including capitalisation)
- [ ] The product/feature mentioned in paragraph 1 actually exists and works as described
- [ ] The JD reference in paragraph 2 is accurate (not from a different company's JD)
- [ ] The portfolio URL works and links to the right project
- [ ] No "paste error" placeholder text remains (e.g. "[Company Name]" still visible)
- [ ] Word count is under 320 words
- [ ] Tone feels like you — not like ChatGPT wrote it

